-- ============================================================
-- Airline Reservation System (AirBooking)
-- CSE 305 Term Project — Sample Seed Data
-- ============================================================
-- Execute AFTER: 01_schema.sql → 02_functions.sql → this file
-- SEAT_INVENTORY rows are auto-generated by the trigger on SEAT_CLASS INSERT.
--
-- Readable UUID Scheme:
--   Airports  → ...0101 ~ 0105
--   Airlines  → ...0201 ~ 0203
--   Aircraft  → ...0301 ~ 0303
--   SeatClass → ...0401 ~ 0409
--   Schedules → ...0501 ~ 0504
--   Customers → ...0601 ~ 0602
--   Staff     → ...0701
--   Stopovers → ...0801
-- ============================================================


